10. Daily Reporting & Notifications

10.1 Daily Build Report
Every morning before 7:00 AM local time, the Reporting Engine generates and delivers a comprehensive Daily Build Report to all project stakeholders. The report is generated by scanning the Trello board state, internal project data, weather forecasts, and vendor communication logs.

Report Contents

Section
Content
Data Source
Executive Summary
1-paragraph AI-written summary of yesterday and today
Trello + Internal DB
Progress Tracker
Tasks completed yesterday, tasks active today, tasks starting tomorrow
Trello Board Scan
