The database schema is organized around six primary entity groups: Users & Organizations, Projects & Phases, Design Artifacts, Vendors & Contracts, Trello Sync State, and Disputes & Resolutions. All entities include standard audit columns (created_at, updated_at, created_by) and soft-delete support.

