14. API Specification

14.1 API Design Principles
The VibeHouse API follows RESTful conventions with JSON payloads, using OAuth 2.0 + JWT for authentication. All endpoints are versioned (v1), rate-limited, and documented via auto-generated OpenAPI 3.1 specifications. WebSocket endpoints are available for real-time updates.

