Impact
Mitigation Strategy
AI-generated plans contain structural errors
Medium
Critical
Mandatory professional engineer review for all structural calculations. Liability insurance. Phased rollout with human-in-the-loop validation.
Trello API rate limits constrain scaling
High
High
Implement aggressive caching, webhook-first architecture, batch API calls. Evaluate migration to custom board at Phase 3.
Contractors refuse to adopt Trello workflow
Medium
High
Provide lightweight mobile companion app. Allow SMS/email-only interaction with AI translating to board updates. Incentive program for early adopters.
